CONNECTONS:-
| Component       | RPi Pin (Physical) | GPIO Number | Connection Description                             |
| --------------- | ------------------ | ----------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| LED Anode (+)   | Pin 12             | GPIO18      | Positive leg of LED (with 220Î© resistor in series) |
| LED Cathode (-) | Pin 6              | GND         | Ground connection                                  |



CODE:-
import RPi.GPIO as GPIO
import time

LED_PIN = 18  # GPIO18 (Pin 12)
GPIO.setmode(GPIO.BCM)
GPIO.setup(LED_PIN, GPIO.OUT)

while True:
    GPIO.output(LED_PIN, GPIO.HIGH)
    time.sleep(1)
    GPIO.output(LED_PIN, GPIO.LOW)
    time.sleep(1)
